</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Territorial<br />
changes</th>
<td>Britain recognizes independence of the United States, cedes <a href="/wiki/East_Florida" title="East Florida">East Florida</a>, <a href="/wiki/West_Florida" title="West Florida">West Florida</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Minorca" title="Minorca">Minorca</a> to Spain and <a href="/wiki/Tobago" title="Tobago">Tobago</a> to France</td>
