<div style="padding: 0.2em 0; line-height: 1.3em;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong class="selflink">Campaigns and theaters</strong></span></div>
</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px;">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Boston_campaign" title="Boston campaign">Boston</a> – <a href="/wiki/Invasion_of_Canada_(1775)" title="Invasion of Canada (1775)">Canada</a> – <a href="/wiki/New_York_and_New_Jersey_campaign" title="New York and New Jersey campaign">New&#160;York&#160;and&#160;New&#160;Jersey</a> – <a href="/wiki/Saratoga_campaign" title="Saratoga campaign">Saratoga</a> – <a href="/wiki/Philadelphia_campaign" title="Philadelphia campaign">Philadelphia</a> – <a href="/wiki/Western_theater_of_the_American_Revolutionary_War" title="Western theater of the American Revolutionary War">Western</a> – <a href="/wiki/Northern_theater_of_the_American_Revolutionary_War_after_Saratoga" title="Northern theater of the American Revolutionary War after Saratoga">Northern</a> – <a href="/wiki/Southern_theater_of_the_American_Revolutionary_War" title="Southern theater of the American Revolutionary War">Southern</a> – <a href="/wiki/Siege_of_Yorktown" title="Siege of Yorktown">Yorktown</a> - <a href="/wiki/American_Revolutionary_War#Widening_of_the_naval_war" title="American Revolutionary War">West&#160;Indies&#160;and&#160;Gulf&#160;Coast</a> – <a href="/wiki/Naval_operations_in_the_American_Revolutionary_War" title="Naval operations in the American Revolutionary War">Naval</a></div>
</td>
